[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Active : reject
Cancelled : entry / log deliverynote
Active --> Created : process
Created --> Shipped : update
Shipped --> Draft : review
Draft --> Closed : approve
Active --> Cancelled : revert
Closed --> [*]
